I am [http://samueltonini.com/ samueltonini], a software developer and dance teacher.

These days I have been coding heavily with Elixir, Emacs Lisp, Ruby and JavaScript.

Since a [http://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/senny friend] introduced me to Emacs, I use Emacs every day all the time for everything.




