== My Emacs configuration ==
My Emacs setup is based on [[cabbage]]

[[cabbage]] fundamental organization are bundles. You can enable and disable the configuration on a per bundle basis.

Have a look at my [https://github.com/tonini/emacs.d config] and see how you could setup everything properly through bundles.

